name: 美少女万華鏡－罪と罰の少女－覡 夕莉 / Bishojo Mangekyo－Tsumi to Batsu no Shoujo－ Kannagi Yuuri / 美少女万华镜－罪与罚的少女－ 覡夕莉
description:
2023,04,21 v2.0

两个衣服能正常画出来了，私服那个白黑+红裙子的难画出来。

大衣：Kannagi-Yuuri-co, red coat

水手服：Kannagi-Yuuri-se, serafuku

私服：Kannagi-Yuuri-pc, red skirt

Google Translate:

The two clothes can be drawn normally, it is difficult to draw the white and black + red skirt in casual clothes.

Coat: Kannagi-Yuuri-co, red coat

serafuku: Kannagi-Yuuri-se, serafuku

Private Clothes: Kannagi-Yuuri-pc, red skirt

OLD v1.0

TAG乱套了，以后再更新吧，练了四个衣服怎么写触发词都只能画出一个校服，但衣服触发词不写只写人名到时能随机出来别的衣服......?，换衣服请用0.4及以下的强度不写提示词

Kannagi Yuuri, , serafuku, coat, civies, nightshirt.

Google Translate:

The prompt words are messed up, I will update them later when I have time, I have trained four clothes, but no matter how I write the prompt words, I can only draw one school uniform.

But if you don’t write the prompt words for clothes, just write the name of the character, and other clothes will appear randomly...?, please use an intensity below 0.4 to change clothes
